---
title: "_setAuction (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_checkZero: auction == address(0)
    q_checkZero --> q_revertZero: auction is zero
    q_checkZero --> q_checkInterface: auction is non-zero
    q_revertZero --> [*]: revert Errors.InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_checkInterface --> q_revertInterface: !supportsInterface(IBaseAuction)
    q_checkInterface --> q_checkDuplicate: supportsInterface(IBaseAuction)
    q_revertInterface --> [*]: revert InvalidAuctionContract(auction)
    q_checkDuplicate --> q_revertDuplicate: address(s_auction) == auction
    q_checkDuplicate --> q_store: address(s_auction) != auction
    q_revertDuplicate --> [*]: revert Errors.ValueNotUpdated()
    q_store --> q_emit: s_auction = IBaseAuction(auction)
    q_emit --> [*]: emit AuctionContractSet(auction)

    note right of q_checkInterface
        INV-001: auction must implement IBaseAuction (ERC-165 check)
        INV-002: setting same auction address twice is rejected
        INV-003: zero address is rejected before interface check
    end note
